TEXT.S: = Sayie = Gaga mniq Sincuseyn Ufungsyang ka alang Sayie. 27 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 70 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 96% niqan 67 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 4% niqan 3 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Saysiyat 74%, Tayal 16%, Amis 1%, Paiwan 4%.
